    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a mechanically sorted 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six and a precise 6-speed manual gearbox. This driver\u2019s example has undergone essential preventative maintenance, including a comprehensive VANOS system overhaul and rear subframe reinforcement to ensure chassis integrity under high lateral loads. The engine pulls strongly to its 8,000 RPM redline, benefiting from crisp throttle response via its individual throttle bodies. Handling remains sharp thanks to refreshed control arm bushings and a functional M Variable Differential Lock. While the finish shows minor road-wear, the drivetrain and suspension geometry are dialed for peak performance. A robust, analog machine ready for the canyons.",
