    {
      "id": "sybil_8_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_8",
      "description": "Up for sale is a meticulously maintained vehicle that offers a fantastic balance of performance and comfort. The exterior is finished in a timeless coat that still holds a deep shine; while there are a few minor stone chips on the hood and a small scuff on the rear passenger wheel arch, the body remains straight and free of any major dents. Inside, the cabin is exceptionally clean and has never been smoked in. The leather seats show only light natural wear on the driver-side bolster, and all interior electronics\u2014including the dual-zone climate control and navigation system\u2014are fully operational. Mechanically, this car is in great shape. It has a complete service history, with the most recent maintenance including a fresh oil change and a cooling system flush. The tires have approximately 70% tread life remaining, and the brakes provide firm, confident stopping power. This is a reliable, turn-key vehicle perfect for someone looking for a high-quality driver without the premium price of a brand-new model.",
